<paragraph blockId="142.[151,1437,764,1223]" box="[151,497,945,972]" pageId="142" pageNumber="143">Larval host plant(s): unknown.</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="142.[151,1437,764,1223]" box="[151,385,981,1008]" pageId="142" pageNumber="143">
